      <title>利润降温令印度股市创纪录的 11 个月涨势面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/india-s-record-11-month-stock-rally-is-at-risk-as-profits-cool</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近几个月来，印度股市一路走高，因为盈利飙升抵消了人们对高估值的担忧。但随着公司预计利润增长放缓，这种势头面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/india-s-record-11-month-stock-rally-is-at-risk-as-profits-cool</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 01:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
